article.headline: South Carolina State earns 72-61 victory against Morgan State
article.description: — Raquan Brown and Michael Teal each scored 12 points and South Carolina State beat Morgan State 72-61 on Saturday night.
article.linkText: South Carolina State earns 72-61 victory against Morgan State
article.story: BALTIMORE -- — Raquan Brown and Michael Teal each scored 12 points and South Carolina State beat Morgan State 72-61 on Saturday night. Brown was 5 of 11 shooting (1 for 4 from 3-point range) for the Bulldogs (13-16, 8-4 Mid-Eastern Athletic Conference). Teal added 12 points while going 4 of 9 and 3 of 3 from the free throw line, and also had three steals. Wynston Tabbs finished with 13 points for the Bears (9-19, 5-7). Will Thomas added nine points for Morgan State. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
